Based on the AURUM Partner Program compensation plan, a structure where each person has
three legs (branches) is not only feasible but is mechanically necessary to reach the highest
leadership ranks.
While the program technically allows you to start with just two branches to reach early levels like
AURUM Vanguard , the requirements shift toward a three-branch minimum once you aim for
the upper half of the 15 Legacy Levels
