Strategic Advantages of the 3-Leg Structure
●
Maximizing "Difference Bonuses": You earn the difference between your Legacy
Level percentage and the highest percentage in your team. Spreading volume across
three legs instead of one or two deep lines often allows you to maintain a higher
percentage gap over more people, increasing your Team Sales income.
●
●
Unlocking the Shareholder Bonus: To qualify for the global Shareholder Pool
(quarterly bonuses of up to 3.125% of global profits), you must reach the rank of
AURUM Oracle or higher. Building three legs early ensures you don't get "stuck" below
Oracle due to a lack of branch diversity.
Volume Efficiency: Since Legacy Volume (LV) represents only 40% of the actual sales
made in your team , having three active legs helps accumulate the massive volume
needed for higher ranks more reliably than relying on just one or two "superstars"
Summary Recommendation
Building with three legs per person is the most efficient way to navigate this plan. It satisfies
the mandatory "3 different branches" rule for the middle and upper-middle ranks while providing
the broad volume base required to capture the 18.5% maximum Direct Sales commission and
the 30% maximum ProfitShare at the AURUM Alpha level.